node.text: I wanted to hop on here and express just how much I love and value you all, since I wasn’t able to give my whole thanks on stage ❤️We won Best Movie BECAUSE of you all and I wanted to express just how grateful I am to every single one of you ❤️. Thank you endlessly!

node.text: I am BEYOND thrilled to finally announce I am the newest face and brand ambassador for @neutrogena !!! I am thrilled to partner with Neutrogena 😍😭. I’ve waited so long to tell you all the news and I couldn’t be more excited to finally share. I have been a true fan of the brand for as long as I’ve known about skincare and it’s truly an honor to be able to work with them! Here we go! #NTGSpokesperson
